Open the Application in Your Browser:
Navigate to http://localhost:3000 in your web browser.

Log In:

Enter your credentials to log in.
Usage
Enter Addresses:

Input addresses in the provided text fields on the main page (index.html).
Click "Add Another Address" to dynamically add more address input fields.
Get Map Polygon:

After entering addresses, click the "Submit Addresses" button to geocode them and store the data.
Distance Calculation:

The application calculates and logs the distance between consecutive addresses.
Cumulative distance and motorable paths are displayed on the map on the second-page.html.
Logout:

Click the "Logout" button to log out from the application.


